      "Txt_Talk_Portoga_Castle_1F_SUB_0_ACTOR_0510_010_1": {
        "SelfId": "Txt_Talk_Portoga_Castle_1F_SUB_0_ACTOR_0510_010_1",
        "Text": "聽說東邊有個神殿，\r\n竟然可以在那裡改變職業。"
